    <name>NoLimitConnect</name>
    <summary>Social Network</summary>
    <description>
        <p>NoLimitConnect is a full featured social network.</p>
        <p>A independent social network designed to be hosted on any device with an internet connection.</p>
        <p>Major features:
        o Person to Person and plugin permissions: Ignore, Guest, Friend, Admin
        o Push To Talk VOIP
        o Stream shared media files
        o Share and transfer files (No file size limit)
        o Video Chat
        o VOIP Voice Phone
        o Messenger
        o About Me user page
        o Storyboard blog page
        o Web Cam Server
        o Media Player
        o Chat Room host and client
        o Random Connect host and client
        o Group host and client</p>
    </description>
